snippet.title: Flip Out Rush: LITE (PC Edition) - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD THE DEMO HERE: https://gamejolt.com/games/flipoutrush/949520

Flip Out Rush is coming to PC with Flip Out Rush LITE!

The mobile game Flip Out Rush arrives for the very first time to PC on all platforms! Allowing you to rush as much as you can with the power of your PC and/or laptop! Play the PC Demo today with Flip Out Rush Lite!

Endless Fun is here!

Flip Out Rush is a classic styled endless runner game where the fun (and running) never stops! Rush, Jump, collect coins and flip your way through randomly generated levels to get the highest score possible!

Song:
ko0x - Galaxy Guppy: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mIrqWhIx6vs

--------------------------------------
